0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"燒碳食安眠藥"},{"pid":"755edede06ccfd2f2b1d194930917a4f6cb4bf9a","tid":1677970,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39a6f92722a901661e998a2e9965aa089a35d98","tid":1677970,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"自殺式襲擊"},{"pid":"fa2bcd8d3d8aaad3a982e3222ce8129aaa1cf33c","tid":1677970,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n鐘庭耀發起全港性民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=9890474e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"9cd0f6faddded75cadb79a45afe8414beebdce4e","tid":1677970,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"約朋友玩 開心死"},{"pid":"5ad37d8591f3c4301c5ba6c1ebc746f1fb16ac67","tid":1677970,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2232476d600bb0d8b031f3554094f7013bee0785","tid":1677970,"uid":274591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:50:01.000Z","msg":"跳軌定跳樓成功率大啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n <br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=cd0a684e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"2bffe884a3dfe61f91184ab47d3cbf10c5100d37","tid":1677970,"uid":92435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"唔想知"}]}